## Description {#details}

Evaluate the size and offset of an object pointed to by a Value&#42;.

May create code to compute the result at run-time.

Definition at line 327 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/analysis/memorybuiltins-h">MemoryBuiltins.h</a>.
